title: Razia Sultan
subTitle: Razia Sultan, the first female ruler of the Delhi Sultanate, lands in trouble and loses her kingdom when she falls in love with Jamal-ud-Din Yakut, an Abyssinian slave.

title: Anita
subTitle: When Anita commits suicide, Neeraj suspects foul play and decides to investigate the truth. However, things take a turn when he starts seeing Anita everywhere.

title: Chalti Ka Naam Gaadi
subTitle: Brijmohan, a mechanic, swears off women after a bad experience. However, when a headstrong woman arrives at his garage, he is forced to reconsider his opinion.

title: Bhuvan Shome
subTitle: A lonely bureaucrat goes on holiday to a village in Gujarat where a young peasant woman helps him see beyond his job and develop a newfound empathy for people.

title: Woh 7 Din
subTitle: Anand, a doctor, realises that Maya, his wife, loves someone else but married him out of coercion. Thus, he sets out to reunite the lovers, but they don't want to be together anymore.

title: Kalicharan
subTitle: When Prabhakar, an honest cop, is murdered by Din Dayal, a powerful crime lord, Khanna recruits his doppelganger Kalicharan to defeat Din Dayal.

title: Pukar
subTitle: Major Jaidev saves a politician from the clutches of a dreaded terrorist. However, the terrorist joins hands with his childhood friend Anjali to ruin his life.

title: Bobby
subTitle: Raja, the son of a rich Hindu businessman, falls in love with Bobby, a poor Catholic girl. Though their families try to keep them away from each other, they strive to be together.

title: Kuchhe Dhaage
subTitle: To avenge his father's death, Lakhan kills Roopa's father, Tulsiram, in cold blood. Enraged, Roopa decides to kill him, but fate has its own plans.

title: Saagar
subTitle: Raja secretly loves Mona, but she is in love with Ravi. However, Ravi's grandmother disapproves of their relationship and asks Mona to forget him and marry someone else.

title: Honeymoon
subTitle: A couple's idyllic lake honeymoon turns chaotic when the husband discovers his wife disoriented in the night, unleashing unforeseen turmoil.

title: Narsingh Avatar
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Chitchor
subTitle: When Geeta's sister arranges her wedding with a young engineer, their father mistakenly brings the wrong man home. However, as love blossoms between the two, the arrival of a letter startles everyone.

title: Chameli Ki Shaadi
subTitle: Charandas and Chameli develop feelings for each other. However, caste differences lead their families to oppose their budding relationship.

title: Waris
subTitle: Frustrated by the king's behaviour, the queen leaves the kingdom with her son. Years later, when the king dies, the palace officials search for his son to claim the throne.

title: Humjoli
subTitle: Gopaldas, a villager, dreams of becoming rich and, thus, marries Roopa, an heiress. However, his greed knows no bounds when he plots Roopa's murder to inherit her property.

title: Kasam Suhaag Ki
subTitle: Troubles arise for Surajmukhi after her husband, Sultan, is gunned down and she and her daughter get abducted by goons. She tries her best to get revenge and escape with her child.

title: Mard
subTitle: Azad, a wealthy prosperous king, is locked in a dungeon by General Dyer who wants to take over his kingdom. Years later, Azad's son comes to his father's rescue and puts an end to Dyer's tyranny.

title: Karz
subTitle: Monty discovers the shocking truth about his past life when he was killed by his gold-digger wife, while his family was rendered homeless. Supported by his lover, he decides to set things right.

title: Karz
subTitle: Monty discovers the shocking truth about his past life when he was killed by his gold-digger wife, while his family was rendered homeless. Supported by his lover, he decides to set things right.

title: Kunwara Baap
subTitle: A rickshaw driver's life changes when he finds an abandoned baby at his doorstep. When the child is affected by polio, he has a change of heart and decides to care for him.

title: Saaransh
subTitle: When Pradhan and Parvati lose their son, they open their home to Sujata Suman, a struggling actress. Her presence brings comfort and renewed hope to the mourning parents.

title: Naqab
subTitle: Imran, a freelance photographer, meets Asiya, a mysterious woman, on his way to Alipur for an assignment. However, things take a turn when he repeatedly sees her and starts to question reality.

title: Razia Sultan
subTitle: Razia Sultan, the first female ruler of the Delhi Sultanate, lands in trouble and loses her kingdom when she falls in love with Jamal-ud-Din Yakut, an Abyssinian slave.

title: Sharmeelee
subTitle: A man meets a girl at a rest house and falls in love with her. However, on the day of their marriage, he is shocked to be betrothed to her twin sister.

title: Sheshnaag
subTitle: Pritam and Banu, two shape-shifting snakes in human form, seek protection from a young man when an evil priest tries to hunt them down and use them in a ritual for wealth and immortality.

title: Do Chor
subTitle: Tony, a burglar, comes under the radar of suspicion when a series of mysterious thefts bewilder the police. Soon enough, he tries to redeem his honour by going after the real criminal.

title: Anjaana
subTitle: Raju, a garage mechanic, falls in love with Rachna but her guardian, Diwan, opposes the marriage and humiliates Raju's mother. Raju decides to exact his revenge against Diwan and teach him a lesson.
